<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Mitchell 01 [Gordon R., Member of the Center for Strategic and International Studies Working Group on Theater Missile Defenses in the Asia-Pacific Region., Winter “Japan-U.S. Missile Defense Collaboration: Rhetorically Delicious, Deceptively Dangerous”,http://www.pitt.edu/~gordonm/JPubs/JapanTMD.pdf] </span></span>
