<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span class="Underline"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"> THEIR RHETORIC OF ENVIRONMENTAL CRISIS DRIVES A LOGIC OF ENVIRONMENTAL SECURITY THAT DEMANDS INEFFECTIVE STATE RESPONSES TO MANAGE ENVIRONMENTAL THREATS </span></span></span>
<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span class="Underline"><span style="text-decoration: none;"><span style="font-family: Georgia;"> </span></span></span></span>
<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span class="Underline"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Ole Waever, 95,  </span></span></span>
<span style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt;"><span class="Underline"><span style="font-family: Georgia;">Senior Researcher at the Center for Peace & Conflict Research, On Security, p. 63-64 </span></span></span>
